        <div class="content-column lang-en">
            <h3>ЁЯЗмЁЯЗз ENGLISH</h3>
            <div class="question-style">What are the Commonwealth Games?</div>
            <div class="answer-style">
                тЖР <span class="highlight-imp">A grand sports festival</span> of the 
                <span class="highlight-imp">Commonwealth of Nations member countries</span> and the 
                <span class="highlight-imp">British Empire</span>, which is governed by the 
                <span class="highlight-critical">British Empire</span>.
            </div>
            
            <div class="question-style">Who first came up with the idea? <span class="highlight-imp">1891</span></div>
            <div class="answer-style">
                This idea came to <span class="highlight-imp">Father Reverend Astley Cooper</span>. 
                The idea was published in a magazine called "<span class="highlight-imp">The Times</span>".
            </div>
        </div>
        
